# Hosted connector — operator-generated artifacts. The README + wrangler.toml.example
# tell operators to create these REAL files inside connector/worker/ (their private
# workspace snapshot, their deploy config, their local secrets) and "never commit"
# them. Enforce that here so a stray `git add .` cannot leak them. The committed
# *.example variants are intentionally not matched and stay tracked.
connector/worker/agentctx.snapshot.json
connector/worker/wrangler.toml
.dev.vars
# Claude Code local session settings (session-scoped permissions — never commit)
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/worktrees/
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
